Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:36.55,CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&H678ABA&\bord0\shad0\an8\fs16\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\b0}中文翻译：肥羊菌_\N翻译自英语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:43.43,JP,,0,0,0,,君の髪に冬の残り香があった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:49.38,JP,,0,0,0,,ほろ苦くて、煙みたいなアイスブルーで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:54.70,JP,,0,0,0,,僕の髪に春の花びらがついて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.51,JP,,0,0,0,,笑い合っていたこと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:01:01.65,JP,,0,0,0,,もう随分前のことのように思える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:05.90,JP,,0,0,0,,あまりに脆くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:12.40,JP,,0,0,0,,ただ散りゆく季節の幼い恋を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:17.05,JP,,0,0,0,,胸に抱いて雨を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:27.48,JP,,0,0,0,,花冷えの日、またひとつ春めいていくから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:32.73,JP,,0,0,0,,さらさらと頬を撫でる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:38.64,JP,,0,0,0,,春の雨にまた君を思い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:48.68,JP,,0,0,0,,薄桃色に霞んでいく光の束をつかんだら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:53.67,JP,,0,0,0,,花便りがもう聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:58.89,JP,,0,0,0,,昼下がりの街はグレイスケールの海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.70,JP,,0,0,0,,こぬか雨だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.56,JP,,0,0,0,,傘をさしたって仕方ないね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:10.04,JP,,0,0,0,,笑う君の長いまつ毛を滑った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:12.78,JP,,0,0,0,,しずくになれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.01,JP,,0,0,0,,そんな空想さえ懐かしく思える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:21.09,JP,,0,0,0,,僕らの時間は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:27.93,JP,,0,0,0,,ただ散りゆく季節と共に過ぎていった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:35.52,JP,,0,0,0,,気づけば君の背中は春霞の向こう側
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:40.06,JP,,0,0,0,,逃げ去ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:45.27,JP,,0,0,0,,さらさらと頬を撫でる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:51.21,JP,,0,0,0,,春の雨にまた君を思い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:55.79,JP,,0,0,0,,アスファルトに滲んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:03:01.31,JP,,0,0,0,,花びらひとつ拾う度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:12.80,JP,,0,0,0,,何度も踏みつけられて汚れてもなお鮮やかな桃色が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:19.43,JP,,0,0,0,,あの日から色のない霧に囚われた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:24.74,JP,,0,0,0,,僕の目には眩し過ぎたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:34.85,JP,,0,0,0,,季節が千巡っても、またここに戻ってこようと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:41.30,JP,,0,0,0,,花冷えの日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:46.62,JP,,0,0,0,,さらさらと頬に伝う
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:52.59,JP,,0,0,0,,しずくはもう溢れてしまって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:56.78,JP,,0,0,0,,景色全部が滲んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:04:03.77,JP,,0,0,0,,君の背中が見えた気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:08.91,JP,,0,0,0,,さらさらと頬を撫でる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:14.89,JP,,0,0,0,,春の雨にまた君を思い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:25.10,JP,,0,0,0,,薄桃色に霞んでいく光の束をつかんだら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:29.88,JP,,0,0,0,,花便りがもう聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:35.18,JP,,0,0,0,,ぬるい風に冬の残り香があった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.83,JP,,0,0,0,,何度だって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:46.07,JP,,0,0,0,,君のいない春を歩いていくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.08,JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:31.25,EN,,0,0,0,,I wrote a song called "Chiharu." Please listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:43.43,EN,,0,0,0,,The scent of winter lingers in your hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:49.38,EN,,0,0,0,,It's bittersweet and a smokey ice blue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:54.70,EN,,0,0,0,,When spring flower petals caught in my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.51,EN,,0,0,0,,We laughed together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:01:01.65,EN,,0,0,0,,Seems like such a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:05.90,EN,,0,0,0,,Such fragility
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:12.40,EN,,0,0,0,,Young love in the twilight season
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:17.05,EN,,0,0,0,,Holding it close to my heart, I wait for rain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:27.48,EN,,0,0,0,,A cold day during the cherry blossoms brings us closer to spring
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:32.73,EN,,0,0,0,,When my cheeks are softly caressed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:38.64,EN,,0,0,0,,By a spring rain, I'm reminded of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:48.68,EN,,0,0,0,,When I grasp a bundle of light, turning into a mist of pale pink
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:53.67,EN,,0,0,0,,I can hear the tidings of flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:58.89,EN,,0,0,0,,The city in the early afternoon is a greyscale ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.70,EN,,0,0,0,,A light rain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Umbrellas make no sense
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:10.04,EN,,0,0,0,,Hoping to turn into droplets that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:12.78,EN,,0,0,0,,Slipped off your long lashes as you laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.01,EN,,0,0,0,,Now I look back fondly on such fantasies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:21.09,EN,,0,0,0,,Our time with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:27.93,EN,,0,0,0,,Passed by together with the dispersing seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:35.52,EN,,0,0,0,,By the time I noticed, you'd already turned back and was way beyond the spring mist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:40.06,EN,,0,0,0,,You'd run away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:45.27,EN,,0,0,0,,When my cheeks are softly caressed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:51.21,EN,,0,0,0,,By a spring rain, I'm reminded of you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:55.79,EN,,0,0,0,,Blurring into the asphalt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:03:01.31,EN,,0,0,0,,Every time I pick up a flower petal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:12.80,EN,,0,0,0,,A bright pink that remains unsoiled no matter how many times it's been trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:19.43,EN,,0,0,0,,Has since that day been taken prisoner by a colorless haze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:24.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Too bright for my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:34.85,EN,,0,0,0,,When the seasons pass a thousand times, I think I'll return to this place again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:41.30,EN,,0,0,0,,On a cold day during the cherry blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:46.62,EN,,0,0,0,,Running down my cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:52.59,EN,,0,0,0,,Are droplets that have overflowed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:56.78,EN,,0,0,0,,All of the scenery before me blurs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:04:03.77,EN,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw your back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:08.91,EN,,0,0,0,,When my cheeks are softly caressed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:14.89,EN,,0,0,0,,By a spring rain, I'm reminded of you again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:25.10,EN,,0,0,0,,When I grasp a bundle of light, turning into a mist of pale pink
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:29.88,EN,,0,0,0,,I can hear the tidings of flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:35.18,EN,,0,0,0,,The scent of winter lingered in a lukewarm wind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.83,EN,,0,0,0,,Again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:46.07,EN,,0,0,0,,I'll walk through spring without you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.08,EN,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:31.25,CN,,0,0,0,,我写了一首叫做《千春》的歌　请听
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:43.43,CN,,0,0,0,,冬日的气息残留于你的发间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:49.38,CN,,0,0,0,,味道有些许苦涩，连同烟雾般的冰蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:54.70,CN,,0,0,0,,初春的花瓣坠在我的发梢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.51,CN,,0,0,0,,我们一同欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:01:01.65,CN,,0,0,0,,仿佛已是许久前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:05.90,CN,,0,0,0,,如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:12.40,CN,,0,0,0,,零散季节中的稚嫩感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:17.05,CN,,0,0,0,,将它关在心间　等待雨的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:27.48,CN,,0,0,0,,花朵盛开期间的寒冷，又将迎来一个春天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:32.73,CN,,0,0,0,,当面颊被轻轻地爱抚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:38.64,CN,,0,0,0,,在这场春雨中　再次回想起了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:48.68,CN,,0,0,0,,在抓住那束淡粉色的霞光之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:53.67,CN,,0,0,0,,便能听闻花的音讯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:58.89,CN,,0,0,0,,午后的街道犹如灰白色的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.70,CN,,0,0,0,,一场细雨到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.56,CN,,0,0,0,,雨伞变得毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:10.04,CN,,0,0,0,,希望我能成为在你欢笑时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:12.78,CN,,0,0,0,,从你那长长的睫毛上滑落下来的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.01,CN,,0,0,0,,我竟然怀念着那种空想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:21.09,CN,,0,0,0,,我们彼此间的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:27.93,CN,,0,0,0,,与消散的季节一同流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:35.52,CN,,0,0,0,,当我回过神来　你已回首　朝着春霞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:40.06,CN,,0,0,0,,逃奔走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:45.27,CN,,0,0,0,,当面颊被轻轻地爱抚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:51.21,CN,,0,0,0,,在这场春雨中　我再次回想起了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:55.79,CN,,0,0,0,,模糊在沥青中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:03:01.31,CN,,0,0,0,,每当拾起一片花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:12.80,CN,,0,0,0,,无论被践踏多少次也不会被污染的淡粉色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:19.43,CN,,0,0,0,,自那天起　我就陷入在了无色烟雾中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:24.74,CN,,0,0,0,,在我的眼中过于耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:34.85,CN,,0,0,0,,即使季节流逝千次，我也想再次回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:41.30,CN,,0,0,0,,在花朵盛开的寒冷日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:46.62,CN,,0,0,0,,顺着我的脸颊流下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:52.59,CN,,0,0,0,,雨滴已经满溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:56.78,CN,,0,0,0,,面前的所有景色都模糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:04:03.77,CN,,0,0,0,,我感觉见到了你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:08.91,CN,,0,0,0,,当面颊被轻轻地爱抚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:14.89,CN,,0,0,0,,在这场春雨中　再次回想起了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:25.10,CN,,0,0,0,,在抓住那束淡粉色的霞光之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:29.88,CN,,0,0,0,,便能听闻花的音讯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:35.18,CN,,0,0,0,,冬日的气息在微温的风中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.83,CN,,0,0,0,,反反复复
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:46.07,CN,,0,0,0,,即使没有你　我也会走过春天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.08,CN,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
